               <msContents class="lemmatic">
                  <summary>This manuscript contains commentary on the book of Aphorisms attributed to <persName type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/287984736" key="person_287984736">Hippocrates</persName>.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="MS_árabe_878-item1">
                     <author key="person_f4517">
                        <persName type="supplied">al-Manāwīالمناوي</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="alt">Taḥqīq al-wuṣūl ʾilā šarḥ al-Fuṣūl</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar">تحقيق الوصول إلى شرح الفصول</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="desc">Facilitating the Understanding of a Commentary on the Aphorisms</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in El Escorial.</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on f. 1b; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 3b; Bk2: 26a; Bk3: 51b; Bk4: 67b; Bk5: 88b; Bk6: 107b; Bk7: 119a.</note>
                     <listBibl>
                        <bibl>
